		<p>
			<h5>
				AmeriQuiz! was designed to be a fun, interactive means for high school students to study American history.  This game was designed in response to the Hidden Agenda project sponsored by Zynga as described <a href="http://facebook.com/haproject" target="_blank">here</a>.
			</h5>
		</p>
	
		<center>
			<h2>How To Play</h2>
		</center>
	
		<p> 
			When you press Play, a significant event from American history will immediately appear at the top of your window.  
			You must enter two pieces of information about each event. 
		</p>
	
		<p>
			<b>FIRST</b>, identify <b>when</b> the event took place by dragging the marker on the scrollbar at the bottom of the map.
		</p>
	
		<p>
			<b>SECOND</b>, identify <b>where</b> the event took place by clicking on the appropriate location on the map.
		</p>
	
		<h4>
			And that's it!  The game will continue for as long as you wish to keep playing.  Good luck, and have fun!
		</h4>
	
